            'content' => '<p>[EDITOR\'S NOTE: This essay is currently being revised following a research trip to the quietest room on Earth (Microsoft\'s anechoic chamber, -20.6 dB). Preliminary conclusion: silence is not the absence of noise. It is the presence of attention. Full essay coming summer 2026.]</p><p>— The Editors</p>',
